so you’re telling me the invincible tardigrade can die because of global warming

40
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:36,540
So, if you too want to fight for the tardigrade cause, I invite you to protect your planet

41
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:41,060
so that even the tiny microscopic world we don’t see can be protected

42
00:02:42,099 --> 00:02:43,630
thanks

43
